                        <a href="https://lailluminator.com/2024/09/03/census-lake-charles/" class="crp_link post-21071"><figure><img width="300" height="200" src="https://lailluminator.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/GettyImages-1269341616-300x200.jpg" class="crp_thumb crp_featured wp-post-image" alt="Chris Johnson sits on the porch of what is left of his home after Hurricane Laura passed through the area on August 28, 2020 in Lake Charles." decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lailluminator.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/GettyImages-1269341616-300x200.jpg 300w, https://lailluminator.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/GettyImages-1269341616-150x100.jpg 150w, https://lailluminator.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/GettyImages-1269341616-768x512.jpg 768w, https://lailluminator.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/GettyImages-1269341616.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px"></figure><span class="crp_title">Census fails to measure impact of natural disasters on Lake Charles</span></a><span class="crp_author">by <a href="https://lailluminator.com/author/zoyateirstein/" title="Posts by Zoya Teirstein, Grist" class="author url fn" rel="author">Zoya Teirstein, Grist</a></span><span class="crp_date">September 3, 2024</span>                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-xxl-4 col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-6">
                        <a href="https://lailluminator.com/2025/01/25/crisis-misinformation/" class="crp_link post-23291"><figure><img width="300" height="200" src="https://lailluminator.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Newsom-fires-300x200.jpg" class="crp_thumb crp_featured wp-post-image" alt="California Governor Gavin Newsom tours the downtown business district of Pacific Palisades as the Palisades Fire continues to burn on Jan. 8, 2025 in Los Angeles." decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lailluminator.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Newsom-fires-300x200.jpg 300w, https://lailluminator.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Newsom-fires-150x100.jpg 150w, https://lailluminator.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Newsom-fires-768x512.jpg 768w, https://lailluminator.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Newsom-fires.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px"></figure><span class="crp_title">In times of crisis, states have few tools to fight misinformation</span></a><span class="crp_author">by <a href="https://lailluminator.com/author/mattvasilogambros/" title="Posts by Matt Vasilogambros" class="author url fn" rel="author">Matt Vasilogambros</a></span><span class="crp_date">January 25, 2025</span>                    </div>
                            </div>
            <div class="crp_clear"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xxl-1 col-xl-1 col-lg-0 col-md-0 col-sm-0 col-0"></div>
</div>
                </div>
            </main></div>
